summary: An ordinance relating to zoning and providing for the rezoning of Lots 11 and 12, Block 12, Supplemental Plat of G. Kinnear's Addition; Lots 14 to 20 inclusive, and vacated alley adjoining, Block 77, Gilman's Addition; Lot 15, Block 38, Gilman's Addition; and Lots 1 to 8 inclusive, Block 96, McNaught's Central Seattle Addition, with respect to Use and Area Districts, and amending Ordinance No. 45382, as amended, by adding thereto two new sections numbered 2-318 and 17-254; respectively.
